// â†’ Why Create Unit Tests?
//
//   It's simple really. It proves that our code really does work, by checking it!
//
//   It's horrible when users complain about bugs with features we created.
//   It almost feels shameful sometimes. But fear not.. unit tests can save us.
//
//   Unit tests are like having an entire testing team just for ourselves. Except we can test
//   much faster! Our testing results are almost instantaneous, delivering immediate reassurance
//   that the app behaves as it was designed to.
//
//   Unit tests exist for us, the developers. They are our tools. What amazing tools
//   they are too. Our unit tests save us so much time exposing our bugs!
//
//   They are just great.
